00:44:30.373 --> 00:44:31.690
the wire now?
 

00:44:31.690 --> 00:44:34.150
What made them move in the DC
circuit?

00:44:34.150 --> 00:44:34.869
Student:  Electric field.
 

00:44:34.869 --> 00:44:35.659
Prof: Electric field.
 

00:44:35.659 --> 00:44:39.460
Look, I want you to understand
that these equations carry a

00:44:39.460 --> 00:44:42.737
large amount of information,
and they in fact carry

00:44:42.737 --> 00:44:45.489
everything as far as you need to
