01:10:15.750 --> 01:10:18.840
These equations have nothing to
do with any loop.

01:10:18.840 --> 01:10:22.135
They just say take a fixed
contour in space and the line

01:10:22.135 --> 01:10:25.729
integral of E on that
contour is the rate of change of

01:10:25.729 --> 01:10:26.270
flux.
 

01:10:26.270 --> 01:10:29.337
It's an intrinsic relation
between electric and magnetic

01:10:29.337 --> 01:10:32.238
fields, not having anything to
do with conductors.

01:10:32.238 --> 01:10:35.551
It's a property of E and
B, namely that a changing

01:10:35.551 --> 01:10:37.970
B can produce a
circulating E.

01:10:37.970 --> 01:10:45.000
That's the content of this
equation.

